step.action:
Build {{product_md}} content from everything captured in steps 2-5:

      "# Product — {{product_name}}

      ## Vision
      {{problem_statement}}

      **Why now:** {{motivation}}

      ## Users
      See personas.md

      ## Desired Outcome
      {{desired_outcome}}

      ## Success Metrics
      {{success_metrics}}

      ## Constraints
      {{constraints}}

      ## Assumptions
      {{assumptions}}

      ## Open Questions
      {{open_questions}}

      ---
      Generated via Nakiros brainstorming workflow on {{date}}. Refresh with /nak-workflow-product-discovery."

Build {{personas_md}} content from {{target_users}} captured in step 4.
    For each persona identified:

      "# Personas — {{product_name}}

      ## {Persona Name}
      {Who they are in one sentence.}
      Needs: {what they need from the product}
      Frustrations: {current pain without this solution}
      Context: {when and how they use the product}

      [repeat for each persona]

      ---
      Generated via Nakiros brainstorming workflow on {{date}}."

Build {{features_list}} from {{scope_v1}} captured in step 5. For each feature identified in scope_v1, prepare a {{feature_md}} with: - slug: lowercase-hyphenated name (used as folder name) - content:
"# Feature: {Feature Name} {What this feature does and the value it brings to users.}
## Capacités prévues {List of capabilities planned for this feature based on the brainstorming session.}
## Dépendances {Other features this depends on, or 'Aucune'}
## Stories | ID | Titre | Statut | |----|-------|--------| | — | À définir | 📋 À planifier |
--- Created via Nakiros brainstorming workflow on {{date}}. Update with /nak-workflow-pm-feature."

Display a structured summary of what will be written:

      "📄 **product.md** — vision, outcome, metrics, constraints
      👥 **personas.md** — {{persona_count}} persona(s) : {{persona_names}}
      🗂 **features/** — {{feature_count}} feature(s) : {{feature_slugs}}

      Here is a preview of the artifacts:

      ---
      **product.md**
      {{product_md}}

      ---
      **personas.md**
      {{personas_md}}

      ---
      **features/**
      {{for each feature: "### {feature_slug}/feature.md\n{feature_md_content}\n---"}}
      "
